description:
Oversize bi-monthly reprint volume published in the UK, with card-stock covers. In addition to the titular Batman/Superman (Vol 2), each issue reprints a selection of Batman- and Superman-related titles. This book replaced the monthly Superman comic, which reprinted issues of Action Comics (Vol 2) in Titan's regular lineup of DC reprints.

Reprinted Titles

The following original print titles have been reprinted in this volume.

  • Batman/Superman (Vol 2) since issue #1
  • Injustice: Gods Among Us since issue #1
  • Superman Unchained since issue #2
  • Adventures of Superman since issue #2
name: Batman/Superman

description:
Archie 1000 Page Comics-Palooza is the latest volume of our biggest-ever collections, featuring over 100 full-color stories in a format similar to the hugely popular Archie Digest series at an amazing price! Follow America's favorite red-head as he navigates the pressures of the American teenager in the awkward, charming and hilarious way you've come to know and love. Features the same mix of wild humor, awkward charm and genuine relatability that has kept Archie and the gang relevant for kids and adults alike for over 70 years. It's 1000 pages of Archie fun at one low price!

Digital chapters for the Archie 1000 Page Comics-Palooza omnibus.
name: Archie 1000 Page Comics-Palooza
